uesta en la ficción, desde el dormitorio de la niña. Al mismo tiempo hace se referencia a que anteriormente se desempeñaba en espectáculos y en su intento por dar el salto a noticias, su exjefa &#8216;Pati&#8217; le exige dar resultados.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"247606\" data-permalink=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/noticias/entretenimiento/los-personajes-de-la-serie-del-caso-paulette/attachment/captura-de-pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20-24-35/\" data-orig-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35.png\" data-orig-size=\"717,376\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35-300x157.png\" data-large-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35.png\" src=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-247606\" srcset=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35.png 717w, https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35-300x157.png 300w, https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-12-a-las-20.24.35-696x365.png 696w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>En ese entonces, Miguel Ángel Mancera se desempeñaba como procurador de justicia de la Ciudad de México, es interpretado por Evelardo Arzate.<br><br>Memo Villegas interpreta a Miranda Nava, quien fue secretario general de gobierno del Estado de México bajo la administración de Enrique Peña Nieto.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra=\'{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/noticias/entretenimiento/los-personajes-de-la-serie-del-caso-paulette/\"}\' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"247616\" data-permalink=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/noticias/entretenimiento/los-personajes-de-la-serie-del-caso-paulette/attachment/captura-de-pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9-58-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9.58.19.png\" data-orig-size=\"438,501\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9.58.19\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9.58.19-262x300.png\" data-large-file=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9.58.19.png\" src=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-Pantalla-2020-06-13-a-las-9.58.19.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"247616\" data-full-url=\"https://fernandafamiliar.soy/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Captura-de-